1001
00:38:37,782 --> 00:38:40,117
Ground pepper.

1002
00:38:40,184 --> 00:38:42,887
All he did so far
was put the dessert in the freezer.

1003
00:38:42,953 --> 00:38:44,655
You don't have much time. Hurry.

1004
00:38:44,722 --> 00:38:45,556
TOAST GROUND PEPPER!

1005
00:38:47,224 --> 00:38:50,194
ADD PASTA WATER IN THE PEPPER

1006
00:38:50,661 --> 00:38:53,164
3. MAKE CHEESE SAUCE
BY MIXING PASTA WATER AND GRANA PADANO

1007
00:38:53,230 --> 00:38:54,265
What's Sam making?

1008
00:38:54,332 --> 00:38:55,599
-<i>Cacio e pepe</i>.
-<i>Cacio e pepe</i> sauce.

1009
00:38:55,666 --> 00:38:57,568
-Cachi…
-<i>Cacio e pepe.</i>

1010
00:38:57,635 --> 00:38:59,437
-Cacho…
-<i>Cacio e pepe.</i>

1011
00:38:59,503 --> 00:39:00,838
Cacho pepe?

1012
00:39:00,905 --> 00:39:04,308
<i>-Cacio e pepe.</i>
<i>-Cacio pepe.</i>

1013
00:39:04,375 --> 00:39:05,543
Cacho e pepepe.

1014
00:39:05,609 --> 00:39:06,744
<i>Cacio e pepe</i>.

1015
00:39:06,811 --> 00:39:08,979
-It's all different.
-I said that.

1016
00:39:09,046 --> 00:39:10,815
"<i>Cacio e pepe</i>."

1017
00:39:10,881 --> 00:39:13,417
-<i>Cacio e pepe</i>.
-<i>Cacio e pepe</i>.

1018
00:39:13,718 --> 00:39:15,152
SCOOP OUT THE PASTA

1019
00:39:15,219 --> 00:39:16,120
Hey!

1020
00:39:16,187 --> 00:39:18,489
Sam's pasta noodles are burnt.

1021
00:39:18,556 --> 00:39:20,524
-I'll pick them out.
-Are the noodles burnt?

1022
00:39:20,591 --> 00:39:21,926
Only beginner pasta cooks do that!

1023
00:39:21,992 --> 00:39:24,462
-It's an emergency!
-The colors are different.

1024
00:39:24,528 --> 00:39:26,130
The Maillard reaction.

1025
00:39:26,197 --> 00:39:27,431
It's the Maillard reaction.

1026
00:39:27,498 --> 00:39:29,600
THE MAILLARD REACTION FOR PASTA?

1027
00:39:29,667 --> 00:39:32,303
That's a mistake
often made by beginner cooks.

1028
00:39:32,370 --> 00:39:36,173
When the pot is too small,
they end up burning the noodles.

1029
00:39:36,240 --> 00:39:38,275
Oh, my. Even after 12 years in LA?

1030
00:39:38,342 --> 00:39:40,411
-What happened?
-I can't believe Sam made that mistake.

1031
00:39:40,478 --> 00:39:42,680
It's an emergency!

1032
00:39:42,747 --> 00:39:44,782
Sung-ju, will you report to us
from the kitchen?

1033
00:39:44,849 --> 00:39:47,017
-Oh, no.
-Let me see whether it's burnt or not.

1034
00:39:47,351 --> 00:39:48,586
