1035
00:39:48,652 --> 00:39:49,787
Time is flying by so fast.

1036
00:39:49,854 --> 00:39:51,355
Will they have enough time?

1037
00:39:53,824 --> 00:39:56,627
What happened to 12 years in LA?

1038
00:39:56,694 --> 00:39:58,062
Look at the pasta. It's dark.

1039
00:39:58,129 --> 00:40:01,098
-Something smells burnt in this area.
-It's fine.

1040
00:40:01,465 --> 00:40:03,667
BURNT PASTA, OUT

1041
00:40:04,568 --> 00:40:06,070
He takes out a few strands.

1042
00:40:06,137 --> 00:40:07,304
WAVES IT OFF

1043
00:40:08,873 --> 00:40:10,841
