Oh, gosh.

1182
00:45:01,832 --> 00:45:04,134
-Okay. Nine. Eight.
-Eight.

1183
00:45:04,201 --> 00:45:06,136
-Seven. Six.
-Seven. Six.

1184
00:45:06,203 --> 00:45:08,205
-Seven. Six.
-Seven. Six.

1185
